Кнопка Connect - set press action: con tcp 192.168.0.1:9876

Кнопка Disconnect - set press action: disconnect

Heartbeat sender - set id: request
                 - set repeat period: 1000

Plot - set id: temp
     - set label: label:temperature=#*1.0C
     - set min: 15
     - set max: 40
     - set length: 60

